{
  "name": "@kernel.chat/kbot",
  "version": "2.19.0",
  "description": "Universal AI agent for your terminal. 39 specialists, 234+ tools, 20 providers. Embedded llama.cpp engine — runs GGUF models directly, no Ollama needed. SWE-bench, HumanEval benchmarks built-in. Auto-context repo mapping. Audit repos, contribute to open source, search arXiv, generate CITATION.cff, audit reproducibility. Academic research tools, scientific computing, data science. Self-evolving, learns your patterns.",
